								<span class="title"><a
										href="https://guardian.ng/news/world/kosovo-president-to-resign-if-war-crimes-charges-confirmed/">Kosovo president to resign if war crimes charges confirmed</a></span>
							</div>
							<div class="excerpt" data-field="excerpt">Kosovo President Hashim Thaci said Monday he would &quot;immediately resign&quot; if a special court in The Hague confirms war crimes charges levied against him last week over his role in Kosovo&#039;s 1990s war.</div>							<div class="meta">
